data.title: Bantam Episodes - 013 - Mudd's Angels
data.meta_description: Bantam Episodes - 013 - Mudd's Angels - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. The Enterprise detects an unidentified vessel evading them. As the vessel enters an asteroid field to lose the Enterprise, its engines overload and fail. To rescue the vessel's crew before they are hit by asteroids, the Enterprise risks overloading its own deflector shields and engines. The crew is able to beam one person aboard - a remarkably fat man named Harry Mudd.
